messages.title: Positive change
messages.content: The SNP will play a constructive role in Westminster and bring ideas forward in a positive spirit.

keyPolicies.policyDescription: Argues that Scotland should not be taken out of the EU against its will.
Opposes NHS privatisation and supports more health investment.
Promises to end austerity with new investments.

issues.brexitEurope: Argues that Scotland should not be taken out of the EU against its will.
issues.economy: Promises to end austerity with new investments.
issues.health: Opposes NHS privatisation and supports more health investment.
issues.socialWelfare: Wants a fairer welfare system and opposes cuts to the Scottish budget.

leaflet.additionalNotes: Leaflet provides general positions of the SNP with a focus on stopping Brexit, protecting the NHS, and ending austerity, but does not include specific candidate details or constituency-level information.
